Package: hystar
Title: Simulation And Least Squares Estimation of the hysteretic TAR Model
Version: 0.0.9
Authors@R: 
    person("Daan", "de Jong", email = "d.dejong@uu.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6034-0136"))
Description: The hysteretic threshold autoregressive (hysTAR) model describes a
    time series that follows one of two possible AR processes according to a
    hysteretic switching mechanism. With 'hystar', you can simulate data from
    this model and estimate parameter values based on empirical or simulated data.
